---
title: Sugar Shack Maple-Black Pepper Double Bacon and Eggs with Savoury Apple-Cheddar Pancakes
description: Maple syrup enthusiasts, look no further than this recipe for that all-Canadian flavour. Classic breakfast vibes meet Quebecois sugar shack decadence in this unbeatable breakfast-for-dinner feast!
